FBIS4-65243 "drweu093_j_94001" FBIS-WEU-94-093 Daily Report 12 May 1994 ITALY & VATICAN CITY Passport of Former Prime Minister Confiscated Passport of Former Prime Minister Confiscated LD1205121394 Rome RAI Uno Television Network in Italian 1130 GMT 12 May 94 LD1205121394 Rome RAI Uno Television Network Italian BFN [Text] Now we have a piece of news just in: Milan examining judge Italo Ghitti has granted a request to confiscate the passport of Bettino Craxi, the former secretary of the Italian Socialists. Craxi is involved in a number of investigations. Yesterday Craxi sent a 21-page report to the judge in which he sought to explain his position.
